<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, December 30 (Xinhua) - Russian Andrei Cherkasov
finished off seeded Italian Renzo Furlan in the first round of the
Australian Hardcourt tennis championship in Adelaide Monday.
</P>
<P>
