<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major Chinese Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 30 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 12 major
Chinese cities for the next 24 hours from 20:00 today to 20:00 on
December 31, issued by China's Central Meteorological Station at
17:00 today:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. -2 degrees c., max. 2 degrees c., clear to light
snow, clam to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shenyang: min. -10 degrees c., max. -3 degrees c., cloudy to
light snow, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin: min. -2 degrees c., max. 2 degrees c., cloudy to light
snow, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Xi'an: min. -4 degree c., max. 4 degrees c., overcast to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Chengdu: min. 8 degrees c., max. 13 degrees c., overcast to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Kunming: min. 3 degrees c., max. 16 degrees c., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Shanghai: min. 4 degrees c., max. 11 degrees c., foggy to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Wuhan: min. 5 degrees c., max. 10 degrees c., foggy to drizzle,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hangzhou: min. 5 degrees c., max. 16 degrees c., foggy to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Taipei: min. 13 degrees c., max. 23 degrees c., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 15 degrees c., max. 25 degrees c., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 17 degrees c., max. 22 degrees c., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze. 
</P>
