has ruled himself out of his scheduled men's singles clash with
Adrian Voinea.
</P>
<P>
However, the 26-year-old Rosset decided to try to partner
Hingis in the mixed doubles, keeping alive Switzerland's hopes of
winning the seven-day contest. 
