<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, December 29 (Xinhua) -- Fourth-seeded France suffered
a surprise 1-2 defeat to unseeded the United States in a Hopman
Cup mixed team tennis tie in Perth on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Unknown 19-year-old Justin Gimelstob, and Chanda Rubin teamed
up to outplay Guy Forget and Mary Pierce 3-6, 6-3, 6-2 in the
